review: Dr Pooja really explained well about the pros and cons of the whitening process before starting. She was extremely genuine, shared multiple whitening options and clearly told what to expect after the treatment. I had some serious stains due to smoking which are now gone and my overall smile is much better. Treatment was completely painless and comforting. Thank you.

tags: Doctor friendliness,Treatment satisfaction,Value for money,Wait time,
review: Very satisfying experience. Quite experienced doctor.  She carried out the treatment with such ease, that the treatment was almost painless and in limited no. of sittings. Was impressed with the cleanliness and the hygiene maintained at the clinic.  I would strongly recommend her for all types of dental treatments.
reply_text: Thanks for the feedback Mr. Deepak. We hope to stand up to ur expectations in future as well.
